Starting point for working on small static sites built on top of Rack so it can be hosted for free on Heroku.

More info: https://devcenter.heroku.com/articles/static-sites-ruby. Has this initial static page setup along with SASS, Bootstrap 2.3.1, and Font Awesome 3.0.2

Demo: http://peaceful-brushlands-2666.herokuapp.com

Other sites that used this as a starting point:
https://github.com/jordanisip/kilimovie (http://kilimovie.com)
https://github.com/jordanisip/jordanisip (http://jordanisip.com)
http://affiliates.tanga.com/